1:25:26.666 --> 1:25:28.541
Gave itself like a secret

1:25:31.291 --> 1:25:33.916
Whispered once more to all of you"

1:25:40.291 --> 1:25:42.416
[applauding]

1:25:42.500 --> 1:25:44.583
